  "texts": [
    "We further integrated the insights gained from the benchmark conducted into developing a new model called MediGuide-14B.",
    "This retrospective study was conducted at the Emergency Chest Pain Centers of the Peking University Third Hospital Group, involving five tertiary-level centers.",
    "The study received ethical approval from the ethics committee of Peking University Third Hospital (M2023828), complying with the Helsinki Declaration.",
    "Chief complaints, current medical history, past medical history, family history, and personal history were extracted from electronic medical records as unstructured text content.",
    "It is important to note that diagnostic test results such as electrocardiograms, myocardial enzyme tests, and echocardiograms were not included in the test dataset provided to the test model and the control group."
  ],
